metadata.name: Hippies #1
metadata.description: Inspired by the hippie image, the photo was created in 2011. This is the main photo from the Hippies collection. This collection has spread all over the world and has been used more than 4,000 times, only on official occasions, in magazines, articles, book covers, etc. Buying photos from this collection, you buy its exclusivity, as well as a piece of its history and add your own.
